items.details: 5 individual servings. Raw - never pasteurized. 3 minute sauce. www.dorot.co.il. No preservatives. Gluten free. All natural.
items.directions: Keep frozen. Pesto sauce - Preparation: Recommended with penne pasta. 1 pasta serving (3.5 oz dry pasta): 1 cube; 3 tsp olive oil. 5 pasta servings (1.1 lbs dry pasta): 5 cubes; 1/4 cup olive oil. 1. Cook pasta according to package instructions. 2. Carefully pour the oil into a pre-heated pot and add the sauce cubes. 3. Melt the cubes in oil for 1-2 minutes. 4. Add cooked pasta and mix. 5. Add salt and grated parmesan cheese to taste. 6. Enjoy and invite your family and friends!
